snippet.title: Gratis Trailer
snippet.description:
A shop has opened, the shopkeep has moved in, and shoppers need assistance. A quick salve, a trifle, salvation. Help them.

Gratis is a short narrative horror-lite game that can be played in about 20-30 minutes with keyboard and mouse.

https://marlowedobbe.itch.io/gratis
